Shop Men's Shoes & Boots

You need comfortable footwear at the office, in the gym, and on out the town. The vast selection of men's shoes at Shoe Carnival features the latest trends in big brand athletic shoes, boots, dress shoes, men's sandals, workwear, and more– all at prices you won't find elsewhere.

Work is a no brainer. If your days are spent at the office, a dapper pair of dress shoes or boots is the way to go. We have brown dress shoes, black dress shoes, and more. Upgrade your workwear with affordable, office-ready men's dress shoes. Tried-and-true styles including wingtips, oxfords, and loafers pair perfectly with suits, slacks, or khakis. Dress boots provide extra support, while work boots and non-slip shoes keep feet protected in unpredictable settings. We also have plenty of wide shoes for men.

Hitting the gym, track, or blacktop keeps your mind sharp and your body ready for anything. Attain your peak performance with the right men's running shoes and footwear from the top athletic brands. Our selection of stylish basketball shoes and sneakers from Nike, New Balance, PUMA, Brooks running shoes, and other great brands are purpose-built so you get the right shoe at a great price.

When you're not working – or working out – it's time to kick back and relax. Comfortable, casual shoes for men from classic brands like Converse, Vans, HEYDUDE, and Crocs are ready for any adventure. For effortless style, men's fashion shoes from Nunn Bush, Rockport, and Sperry make refined, durable options for evenings, weekends…and weekend getaways.

Whether it's a trip to the beach or just to the store, no guy can survive without a solid pair of sandals. Sturdy sandals from Teva, Crocs, and Reef are ideal for afternoons by the water, while sport slides from Nike and Adidas make post-workout plans a treat for your feet.

For any occasion, any time, unbox the best fit! Step out with confidence in the perfect pair of shoes for men from your favorite footwear brands at Shoe Carnival. Because we know that when you look and feel your best, anything is possible when you walk in our shoes. Save on all the men's shoe styles you need with the latest sales on shoes.

Want your footwear faster? Buy online and pickup in-store at a Shoe Carnival store near you. Or have them delivered straight to your door. Shoe Perks members get free shipping on all orders!

Where to Find Men’s Wide Width Shoes

What are some good options for wider shoes? Wide width men's shoes are not only practical, they're stylish too. Find men's wide shoes from top brands like Nike, adidas, Nunn Bush, Skechers, New Balance, Freeman, and many more. Finding the perfect fitting pair of shoes just got easier! Wide options, available at Shoe Carnival, offer a comfortable fit without compromising on style. With an array of stylish options, shopping for shoes is no longer a hassle. Look for slip-on footwear or shoes with laces for a customized fit, and opt for cushioned insoles to keep your feet comfy all day long. Explore Shoe Carnival's collection and discover new favorites that hug your feet just right, making every step a breeze. Whether you have naturally wide feet or simply prefer a little extra room, explore the collection of wide width men’s shoes in store or online at Shoe Carnival.
